		<ul id="basics" class="cd-faq-group"><br><br>
			<li class="cd-faq-title"><h2>Basics</h2></li>
			<li>
				<a class="cd-faq-trigger" href="#0">I forgot my password. How do I restore it?</a>
				<div class="cd-faq-content">
					<p>Due to Kalypso's characteristics, user's security is an our focus. </br>To restore your password, you have to 
	  <%= link_to "follow this procedure", restore_path%>.</p>
				</div> <!-- cd-faq-content -->
			</li>

			<li>
				<a class="cd-faq-trigger" href="#0">How do I sign up in Kalypso?</a>
				<div class="cd-faq-content">
					<p>It is necessary to Sign Up with username, e-mail and password. Kalypso does not store your password and does not use e-mail or username for anything.</p>
				</div> <!-- cd-faq-content -->
			</li>
			<li>
				<a class="cd-faq-trigger" href="#0">QR Code upload doesn't work?</a>
				<div class="cd-faq-content">
					<p>As a recent decision of GOQR, them doesn't allow Allow-Control-Allow-Origin request. So, if you are on Google Chrome and QR Code Upload doesn't work, we suggest you to install the plugin called <a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/allow-control-allow-origi/nlfbmbojpeacfghkpbjhddihlkkiljbi?utm_source=chrome-ntp-icon">Allow-Control-Allow-Origin: *</a>.</p>
				</div> <!-- cd-faq-content -->
			</li>
		</ul> <!-- cd-faq-group -->

		<ul id="mobile" class="cd-faq-group">
			<li class="cd-faq-title"><h2>Mobile</h2></li>
			<li>
				<a class="cd-faq-trigger" href="#0">How does transfer work?</a>
				<div class="cd-faq-content">
					<p>We uses QR Code to transfer your CRYPTED message on your phone without passing on some server, it is a point-to-point connection.</p>
				</div> <!-- cd-faq-content -->
			</li>

			<li>
				<a class="cd-faq-trigger" href="#0">How do I upload text files from my phone or tablet?</a>
				<div class="cd-faq-content">
					<p>You just need to click the download or upload button and write the correct encryption key.</p>
				</div> <!-- cd-faq-content -->
			</li>
		</ul> <!-- cd-faq-group -->

		<ul id="account" class="cd-faq-group">
			<li class="cd-faq-title"><h2>Account</h2></li>
			<li>
				<a class="cd-faq-trigger" href="#0">How do I change my account settings (name, e-mail or password)?</a>
				<div class="cd-faq-content">
					<p>You can go to Settings -> Update your profile.</p>
				</div> <!-- cd-faq-content -->
			</li>

			<li>
				<a class="cd-faq-trigger" href="#0">How do I delete my account?</a>
				<div class="cd-faq-content">
					<p>We let you to easily delete your own account. Just go to Settings -> Update your profile.</p>
				</div> <!-- cd-faq-content -->
			</li>

		</ul> <!-- cd-faq-group -->

